{"tid":180640,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE數學] core/M1/M2 解答區","createTime":"2017-03-31T04:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T09:34:39.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eac6c0305cddde9e226dc00cfc5b6df6eef0f955","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"話說就來考maths/M1/M2<br />\n各位dse考生有野唔識<br />\n可以係度留言問<br />\n我會逐一解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然你唔好期望我會秒回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我解答完你條問題之後<br />\n你要追問<span style=\"color: red;\">同一條</span>問題 請記得quote清楚"},{"pid":"09f23c249a96782dd7946c9aed49da81253a2ebf","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a7687971ee3e6a13794cdc3137de618b0ef9d0","tid":180640,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"唔想知 唔好講<br />\n講咗死全家"},{"pid":"9eb7586e6bce85cf3c7128c27a7f37062a42f134","tid":180640,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1+1 =? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e375cebb4c68c3f0084e355aa5f9b7d60db9218","tid":180640,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mgi75SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgi75SE.jpg&h=c0af1f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/214837_e23bcd57dad73f8462f720150ed11177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F214837_e23bcd57dad73f8462f720150ed11177.jpg&h=6e90a85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲數字ans手寫三個小數不過撳機都係用accurate 嗰個數<br />\n想問計到點解137.914...同25.3865...要reject?"},{"pid":"7c771298516e02a935f2a8a1241c00aeeea66ae3","tid":180640,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:12:14.000Z","msg":"lm 幫手"},{"pid":"8f15b964caf037eb2d123fe28113afbe6c7d5fb6","tid":180640,"uid":34043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"將3拆做3(sin^2(x) + cos^2(x))"},{"pid":"610ff26175c427b61a688236410b1b5add36c351","tid":180640,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將3拆做3(sin^2(x) + cos^2(x))</blockquote><br />\n上面已經計好<br />\n係諗唔明reject 嗰個位"},{"pid":"18b60f4053ef7af186fb1fbcf9ad686210128f11","tid":180640,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mgi75SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgi75SE.jpg&h=c0af1f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/214837_e23bcd57dad73f8462f720150ed11177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F214837_e23bcd57dad73f8462f720150ed11177.jpg&h=6e90a85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲數字ans手寫三個小數不過撳機都係用accurate 嗰個數<br />\n想問計到點解137.914...同25.3865...要reject?</blockquote><br />\n其實LHS同RHS都除(cos theta)^2會快d"},{"pid":"0fb0adbdc7e0a111cfd610fd13336ebfaec26c67","tid":180640,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>將3拆做3(sin^2(x) + cos^2(x))</blockquote><br />\n上面已經計好<br />\n係諗唔明reject 嗰個位</blockquote><br />\n我估係你自乘cos theta會整多咗root"},{"pid":"8f22d1f518e25e785ae8bb86be56fd8df278edb5","tid":180640,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"我計到咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/232000_ee80aa1f54d2193e578c707ee857a141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F232000_ee80aa1f54d2193e578c707ee857a141.jpg&h=2375b91f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c1b5f7075906cf2e7fd6bc74a24e7666b16e755","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>將3拆做3(sin^2(x) + cos^2(x))</blockquote><br />\n上面已經計好<br />\n係諗唔明reject 嗰個位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我舉個例<br />\nsinx=-1<br />\n如果square完變quadratic<br />\n之後再solve返sinx出來會有-1同1<br />\n但到時sinx=1要reject<br />\n而家你個做法大概都係呢個意思<br />\n因為你square完又solve返條quadratic"},{"pid":"99f6e007562db1d93550528b95b105e24dc8af29","tid":180640,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T23:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>將3拆做3(sin^2(x) + cos^2(x))</blockquote><br />\n上面已經計好<br />\n係諗唔明reject 嗰個位</blockquote><br />\n我估係你自乘cos theta會整多咗root</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a4111b24788f3d8596c28b205c335fe8a057aa","tid":180640,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T23:18:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我計到咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/232000_ee80aa1f54d2193e578c707ee857a141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F232000_ee80aa1f54d2193e578c707ee857a141.jpg&h=2375b91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49086aa014774b02173009a3d5647cbd215ce89c","tid":180640,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T23:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>將3拆做3(sin^2(x) + cos^2(x))</blockquote><br />\n上面已經計好<br />\n係諗唔明reject 嗰個位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我舉個例<br />\nsinx=-1<br />\n如果square完變quadratic<br />\n之後再solve返sinx出來會有-1同1<br />\n但到時sinx=1要reject<br />\n而家你個做法大概都係呢個意思<br />\n因為你square完又solve返條quadratic</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8555fb6f63afe4ad2b9a8cde88a988eda15ae1a","tid":180640,"uid":60689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/izcq9x6r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fizcq9x6r&h=0eddd969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691b345058b9237dc467818a1d3ab47f86216334","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T09:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/izcq9x6r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fizcq9x6r&h=0eddd969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下唔好將PQ連埋<br />\n反而畫M同N既locus出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果都唔明 我再畫圖講解"},{"pid":"3d1c606fdb773669084d15ec115833bb6002fc7f","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/izcq9x6r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fizcq9x6r&h=0eddd969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下唔好將PQ連埋<br />\n反而畫M同N既locus出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果都唔明 我再畫圖講解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算啦, 都係教埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91h9L30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91h9L30.png&h=9cc214b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d15de649d5bc65b88fc5ff131c2fe623795c746a","tid":180640,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"m2有咩要溫？"},{"pid":"511ab90ba706b2f1dd5f05248bc9018869ed7740","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>m2有咩要溫？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/194767/page/3?post=0972d025269dfc8c66a1e08f980f036a556843ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/194767/page/3?post=0972d025269dfc8c66a1e08f980f036a556843ba</a><br />\n<br />\n試下做份mock <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047446209ee40d6ad17184fcb8d321622e8b74ba","tid":180640,"uid":104693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>m2有咩要溫？</blockquote><br />\n其實唔洗溫，都係考番平日學到幾多，睇番你水平去到邊。溫得多反而會亂"},{"pid":"8a1c6e8d75e9f75477158810aa8be1c29ea6cd4a","tid":180640,"uid":60689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/izcq9x6r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fizcq9x6r&h=0eddd969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下唔好將PQ連埋<br />\n反而畫M同N既locus出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果都唔明 我再畫圖講解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算啦, 都係教埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91h9L30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91h9L30.png&h=9cc214b3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該哂，畫埋圖好仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左好多都未識，有時d題目重做諗好耐都諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n人蠢讀M2真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63d95f1e4dc28cd689bc523d9dcd185d183cd16","tid":180640,"uid":8976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"點樣操M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a0517129f86d8f56e799c102f66729a4ea424e","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/izcq9x6r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fizcq9x6r&h=0eddd969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下唔好將PQ連埋<br />\n反而畫M同N既locus出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果都唔明 我再畫圖講解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算啦, 都係教埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91h9L30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91h9L30.png&h=9cc214b3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該哂，畫埋圖好仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左好多都未識，有時d題目重做諗好耐都諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n人蠢讀M2真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢條係深返版本amaths slipping rod既問題<br />\n我會覺得出題條友無個樣整個樣<br />\n成條題目想考differentiation<br />\n但考geometry仲深過differentiation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係一條好既評核題目"},{"pid":"bf58be913f0248a909018f9f428d75ad22ca16eb","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣操M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你平時個底點?<br />\n做過幾年pastpaper?"},{"pid":"57be66adaecbc32adb070fd2acb33bb8e8968d1e","tid":180640,"uid":8976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點樣操M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你平時個底點?<br />\n做過幾年pastpaper?</blockquote><br />\nSectionS還可以，一去到SectionS，每條做b part就開始唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做左SP,A maths 2002-2003,呢排努力做緊，但係好多唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78343f7079fbc71bc954b082c4ed0ea5bc1e7a5d","tid":180640,"uid":8976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣操M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你平時個底點?<br />\n做過幾年pastpaper?</blockquote><br />\nSectionA還可以，一去到SectionB，每條做b part就開始唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做左DSE SP,PP,  CE A maths 2002-2003,呢排努力做緊，但係好多唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e69aec6eb4c71ec2099baceb603cd8904cece055","tid":180640,"uid":96831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"M2 5-5*底呢家可以點操到穩一粒星 望兩粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757bfed3125731ed3c5cde402df99851e3dfa0e4","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M2 5-5*底呢家可以點操到穩一粒星 望兩粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nM2最多careless mistake既地方:<br />\ndefinite integral<br />\nmatrix multiplication<br />\n<br />\n起碼唔好錯呢d<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果你matrix唔熟<br />\nsection B做哂其他topic先<br />\n建議做integration&gt;differentiation&gt;vector&gt;matrix"},{"pid":"c4d6ab93cfe59b5868b530a9749914af022b93dc","tid":180640,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"M2做sketching graph<br />\n有咩要注意<br />\n點解有時個graph可以穿過漸近線有時又唔可以?"},{"pid":"6aaa5b17dbb646c0f77e4b5ff012c6ea2ab3f5ea","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T06:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M2做sketching graph<br />\n有咩要注意<br />\n點解有時個graph可以穿過漸近線有時又唔可以?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講個case係horizontal / oblique<br />\n個條asymptote係講緊:<br />\n當x個magnitude越大<br />\nf(x) value越接近漸近線對應既y value<br />\n<br />\n你講緊f(x)穿過漸近線係講緊個x好細既時候<br />\ne.g. x=5 VS x=100000000"},{"pid":"c38c9a33abf99ae6ddfcbefbd0afcb4ac9c64140","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T06:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>M2做sketching graph<br />\n有咩要注意<br />\n點解有時個graph可以穿過漸近線有時又唔可以?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講個case係horizontal / oblique<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">個條asymptote係講緊:<br />\n當x個magnitude越大<br />\nf(x) value越接近漸近線對應既y value</span><br />\n<br />\n你講緊f(x)穿過漸近線係講緊個x好細既時候<br />\ne.g. x=5 VS x=100000000</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充返 呢樣係take limit既concept"},{"pid":"4df9241e02445a49dd84f30b3600668e774a7248","tid":180640,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>M2做sketching graph<br />\n有咩要注意<br />\n點解有時個graph可以穿過漸近線有時又唔可以?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講個case係horizontal / oblique<br />\n個條asymptote係講緊:<br />\n當x個magnitude越大<br />\nf(x) value越接近漸近線對應既y value<br />\n<br />\n你講緊f(x)穿過漸近線係講緊個x好細既時候<br />\ne.g. x=5 VS x=100000000</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思 都係唔太明(太蠢同concept唔清sorry)<br />\n姐係horizontal / oblique 係x好細嘅時候就可以穿過?<br />\n咁我知x幾時算大幾時算細?<br />\n點解垂直線又唔得?"},{"pid":"5f890e368ecd300d1698233bcc53b327cdb61d77","tid":180640,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"我其實大概get到<br />\n但想問清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4286d5b285237ec7aefdcefbd806c26e94f0693","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>M2做sketching graph<br />\n有咩要注意<br />\n點解有時個graph可以穿過漸近線有時又唔可以?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講個case係horizontal / oblique<br />\n個條asymptote係講緊:<br />\n當x個magnitude越大<br />\nf(x) value越接近漸近線對應既y value<br />\n<br />\n你講緊f(x)穿過漸近線係講緊個x好細既時候<br />\ne.g. x=5 VS x=100000000</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思 都係唔太明(太蠢同concept唔清sorry)<br />\n姐係horizontal / oblique 係x好細嘅時候就可以穿過?<br />\n咁我知x幾時算大幾時算細?<br />\n點解垂直線又唔得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你搵horizontal / oblique時候<br />\n係將x take limit架嘛<br />\n如果f (x)係x=5 (example) cut 到條asymptote係無問題<br />\n因為你唔會當x=5談上limit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外 垂直線係無可能穿過<br />\n因為垂直潮近線係講明f(x) not defined on the corresponding value k<br />\nthen x=k係vertical asymptote"},{"pid":"3b0e09c02a0bbe07d79d1ebf76f12eb6ceb81e16","tid":180640,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"Thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6078440a75b241ef88fbace9b5262e1c1efeff37","tid":180640,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"我明你講咩了<br />\n咁我可以點知佢係邊個位會cut到?<br />\n係咪要自己代點?"},{"pid":"083afb2bbab2e4d0a4483a8fc77adaa068d267c8","tid":180640,"uid":96831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>M2 5-5*底呢家可以點操到穩一粒星 望兩粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nM2最多careless mistake既地方:<br />\ndefinite integral<br />\nmatrix multiplication<br />\n<br />\n起碼唔好錯呢d<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果你matrix唔熟<br />\nsection B做哂其他topic先<br />\n建議做integration&gt;differentiation&gt;vector&gt;matrix</blockquote><br />\nmatrix property都唔太差 最近入左matrix inverse matrix 同multiplication program 做matrix有得sub個unknown入去check應該ok穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打覺會唔會tip下今年section b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83b9491f9b37c0696946309f053acad793f85a9","tid":180640,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"Over underestimate 點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1786d4ec162907cee2430cb6615767dd4a6ff9","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Over underestimate 點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講係點證明over/underestimate<br />\n定係搵估值同準備值相差幾多?"},{"pid":"d6bd36bab4fc25868cce46b626fb484fdeb3a0a3","tid":180640,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Over underestimate 點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講係點證明over/underestimate<br />\n定係搵估值同準備值相差幾多?</blockquote><br />\n證明"},{"pid":"402caa717e4349912a1f90ae02d25fec1e7bb35f","tid":180640,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>M2 5-5*底呢家可以點操到穩一粒星 望兩粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nM2最多careless mistake既地方:<br />\ndefinite integral<br />\nmatrix multiplication<br />\n<br />\n起碼唔好錯呢d<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果你matrix唔熟<br />\nsection B做哂其他topic先<br />\n建議做integration&gt;differentiation&gt;vector&gt;matrix</blockquote><br />\nmatrix property都唔太差 最近入左matrix inverse matrix 同multiplication program 做matrix有得sub個unknown入去check應該ok穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打覺會唔會tip下今年section b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入matrix inverse同matrix multiplication完全浪費位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d6815e21f7618b00bebf56bb68b178ac7afff0","tid":180640,"uid":31413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>M2做sketching graph<br />\n有咩要注意<br />\n點解有時個graph可以穿過漸近線有時又唔可以?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講個case係horizontal / oblique<br />\n個條asymptote係講緊:<br />\n當x個magnitude越大<br />\nf(x) value越接近漸近線對應既y value<br />\n<br />\n你講緊f(x)穿過漸近線係講緊個x好細既時候<br />\ne.g. x=5 VS x=100000000</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思 都係唔太明(太蠢同concept唔清sorry)<br />\n姐係horizontal / oblique 係x好細嘅時候就可以穿過?<br />\n咁我知x幾時算大幾時算細?<br />\n點解垂直線又唔得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你搵horizontal / oblique時候<br />\n係將x take limit架嘛<br />\n如果f (x)係x=5 (example) cut 到條asymptote係無問題<br />\n因為你唔會當x=5談上limit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外 垂直線係無可能穿過<br />\n因為垂直潮近線係講明f(x) not defined on the corresponding value k<br />\nthen x=k係vertical asymptote</blockquote><br />\n因為依家學唔係好似以前let y=mx+c take limit搵<br />\n係就咁除左佢 搵條asymptote出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adee82e3067af80fc76808874b118fa8b4861c1e","tid":180640,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"matrix有啲題目係given......prove that......<br />\n有幾十個unknown完全無頭緒點做<br />\n可以點樣諗"},{"pid":"34316dc263db2e9f4b6b1049054650d19e5c2f1d","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Over underestimate 點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講係點證明over/underestimate<br />\n定係搵估值同準備值相差幾多?</blockquote><br />\n證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果f(x)同f&quot;(x) both大過0或者both細過0<br />\n就係over estimate<br />\n如果1個大過0, 1個細過0 就under"},{"pid":"a0384f74a7bb14ae346422bf37a8e8d57498ce13","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>matrix有啲題目係given......prove that......<br />\n有幾十個unknown完全無頭緒點做<br />\n可以點樣諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndse程度既matrix只係入門野<br />\n背後仲有好多concept係out-c<br />\n但往往出題都係考緊呢d out-c concept<br />\n所以你覺得無從入手唔出奇<br />\n因為同你本書學既入門野唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n解決方法:<br />\n做哂sectionB其他題目先<br />\nmatrix放最後做<br />\n拎得幾多分得幾多分"},{"pid":"54f4a0aec8cbf5167cab6bd3f2210b059ec3a065","tid":180640,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明你講咩了<br />\n咁我可以點知佢係邊個位會cut到?<br />\n係咪要自己代點?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有睇書 但書根本冇講清楚<br />\n我都係聽你講先明漸近線做緊咩同點解可以穿過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問點先知佢係邊個位會穿過漸近線?"},{"pid":"d469cabf2438044a7fbea3fa712fd7b3e306b1da","tid":180640,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我明你講咩了<br />\n咁我可以點知佢係邊個位會cut到?<br />\n係咪要自己代點?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有睇書 但書根本冇講清楚<br />\n我都係聽你講先明漸近線做緊咩同點解可以穿過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問點先知佢係邊個位會穿過漸近線?</blockquote><br />\nf(x)同漸近線有intersection point就會穿過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但呢個一定係finite number 唔會有limit呢個概念<br />\n<br />\ncurve sketching畫oblique/horizontal 漸近線其實係睇條線既最左邊(x very negative)同最右邊(x very positive) 因為個到有take limit既意思<br />\n中間個到其實唔關事<br />\n只不過為咗方便sketch<br />\n先會畫埋中間個部分"},{"pid":"8f11507cb3018fe4da0f22a5a1c89a2c0839cb44","tid":180640,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我明你講咩了<br />\n咁我可以點知佢係邊個位會cut到?<br />\n係咪要自己代點?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有睇書 但書根本冇講清楚<br />\n我都係聽你講先明漸近線做緊咩同點解可以穿過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問點先知佢係邊個位會穿過漸近線?</blockquote><br />\nf(x)同漸近線有intersection point就會穿過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但呢個一定係finite number 唔會有limit呢個概念<br />\n<br />\ncurve sketching畫oblique/horizontal 漸近線其實係睇條線既最左邊(x very negative)同最右邊(x very positive) 因為個到有take limit既意思<br />\n中間個到其實唔關事<br />\n只不過為咗方便sketch<br />\n先會畫埋中間個部分</blockquote><br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問太多 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ff7309424df87fd858ba329d2d99954c64b094","tid":180640,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Over underestimate 點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講係點證明over/underestimate<br />\n定係搵估值同準備值相差幾多?</blockquote><br />\n證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果f(x)同f&quot;(x) both大過0或者both細過0<br />\n就係over estimate<br />\n如果1個大過0, 1個細過0 就under</blockquote><br />\n點解要睇埋f(x)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}